description:
Super cute alcove studio in prime LES location. Fully equipped kitchen (with a dishwasher!). Laundry facilities a block away. Any restaurant/venue/store you could possibly need within 5 minute walk or less.

Reachable by phone or email 24/7.

F train is 4 blocks away. 6 train is about an 5 minute walk away.
name: LES Cuteness
